<p>ν• κµ¬λ¬Έμ”© λ³΄μ.</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">let Q be a queue</code>: Queueλ¥Ό μƒμ„±ν•λ‹¤.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">label start_v as discovered</code>: μ‹μ‘ λ£¨νΈ μ •μ μ„ λ°©λ¬Έν‘μ‹ ν•λ‹¤.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">Q.enqueue(start_v)</code>: μ‹μ‘ λ£¨νΈ μ •μ μ„ Queueμ— λ„£λ”λ‹¤.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">while Q is not empty do</code>: Queueκ°€ λΉ κ³µκ°„μ΄ μ•„λ‹ λ• κΉμ§€ μ•„λλ¥Ό λ°λ³µν•λ‹¤.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">v := Q.dequeue()</code>: ν„μ¬ λ°©λ¬Έν•  μ •μ  vλ¥Ό Queueμ—μ„ κΊΌλ‚Έλ‹¤.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">for all edges from v to w in G.adjacentEdges(v) do</code>: vμ™€ μΈμ ‘ν• λ¨λ“  μ •μ  wμ— λ€ν•μ—¬</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">if w is not labeled as discovered then</code>: wκ°€ λ°©λ¬Έν‘μ‹ λμ§€ μ•μ•μΌλ©΄</p>

    <ul>
      <li>
        <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">label w as discovered</code>: wλ¥Ό λ°©λ¬Έν‘μ‹ ν•κ³ </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">Q.enqueue(w)</code>: wλ¥Ό Queueμ— λ„£λ”λ‹¤.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p class="notice--warning">μ„ μμ‚¬μ½”λ“μ—μ„λ” Queueμ— μΈμ ‘ μ •μ μ μ¤‘λ³µ μ €μ¥μ΄ λλ” κ²ƒμ„ λ°©μ§€ν•κΈ° μ„ν•΄ wλ¥Ό Queueμ— λ„£μκ³Ό λ™μ‹μ— λ°©λ¬Έν‘μ‹λ¥Ό ν•΄μ£Όκ³  μλ‹¤.</p>

